# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:15
translate chinese mcgee18_d2594747:

    # "Afterwards, we lie in bed for a moment, catching our breath."
    "之后，我们躺在床上片刻，喘了口气。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:18
translate chinese mcgee18_f4e1b073:

    # mrmg "So, [pcname]..."
    mrmg "那么，[pcname]……"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:19
translate chinese mcgee18_f6b60d54:

    # mrmg "Edie was saying that you're about to graduate. Any plans for after you finish school?"
    mrmg "伊迪说你快毕业了。毕业后有什么打算吗？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:20
translate chinese mcgee18_158b58fb:

    # pc "Oh um... I'm not sure."
    pc "哦，那个……我不确定。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:23
translate chinese mcgee18_338c53f3:

    # et "You're a smart boy. I hope you have some idea of what you're going to do."
    et "你是个聪明的孩子。希望你心里已经有了些打算。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:24
translate chinese mcgee18_a8107df4:

    # mrmg "Yeah, it's good to have a plan. Even if you don't end up sticking to it."
    mrmg "是啊，有计划总是好的。哪怕最后没能坚持下去。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:25
translate chinese mcgee18_67ffd2ed:

    # mrmg "When I was your age, I never would have imagined I'd be running a coffee shop in a small town."
    mrmg "我像你这么大的时候，根本想不到自己会在小镇上开一家咖啡馆。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:26
translate chinese mcgee18_6ed16a5b:

    # et "He wanted to be an architect."
    et "他当时想当建筑师。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:27
translate chinese mcgee18_1f4c7425:

    # mrmg "I couldn't ever wrap my head around the math."
    mrmg "我完全搞不懂那些数学。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:30
translate chinese mcgee18_7dc88a4e:

    # pc "I haven't decided exactly, but I may work in a lab somewhere, like my dad did. Or maybe travel?"
    pc "我还没完全决定，但可能会像我爸那样在某个实验室工作。或者去旅行？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:31
translate chinese mcgee18_a852eda0:

    # mrmg "Well you still have time. As long as you're moving forward, you know?"
    mrmg "嘛，你还有时间。只要你一直在前进，懂吗？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:32
translate chinese mcgee18_81828f00:

    # et "What about romance?"
    et "那感情方面呢？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:33
translate chinese mcgee18_f31c9253:

    # mrmg "Yes, any chance of you settling down soon?"
    mrmg "是啊，你近期有打算安定下来吗？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:38
translate chinese mcgee18_0da9fddf:

    # pc "I have somebody in mind who I might want to settle down with, yeah."
    pc "我心里确实有个人，或许会想和他安定下来，是的。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:39
translate chinese mcgee18_91054e3c:

    # et "That's great."
    et "太好了。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:40
translate chinese mcgee18_039a1f3c:

    # mrmg "Yeah, we're happy for you!"
    mrmg "是啊，我们为你高兴！"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:42
translate chinese mcgee18_3a5905ee:

    # pc "I haven't met anybody yet that I'd want to settle down with."
    pc "我还没遇到想和她共度余生的人。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:43
translate chinese mcgee18_560976b8:

    # et "I'm sure you will. A young girl would be very lucky to be with you."
    et "我相信你会遇到的。能和你在一起的姑娘会非常幸运。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:44
translate chinese mcgee18_5a3cddaa:

    # mrmg "For sure. You'll get your pick of the litter and eventually find someone who checks all the boxes you're looking for."
    mrmg "肯定会。你大可挑挑拣拣，最终会找到那个符合你所有期待的人。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:46
translate chinese mcgee18_313c0671:

    # pc "Why settle, when I can mess around with a bunch of different people?"
    pc "既然能和一大堆不同的人玩玩，何必安定下来？"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:47
translate chinese mcgee18_a1c5c517:

    # mrmg "Haha, it's true, that's fun... for a while."
    mrmg "哈哈，确实，这样挺有趣的……至少暂时是。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:48
translate chinese mcgee18_1e788beb:

    # et "I think that, eventually, you're going to want more though."
    et "但我觉得，到头来，你还是会想要更多。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:51
translate chinese mcgee18_650ed17b:

    # mrmg "Edie and I were just talking about you the other night. About how we hope that you'll find a nice girl to marry."
    mrmg "前几天晚上我和伊迪还在聊你呢。 说我们希望你能找到一个好姑娘结婚。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:52
translate chinese mcgee18_39aeeae4:

    # et "Like we found each other."
    et "就像我们找到彼此那样。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:53
translate chinese mcgee18_1c927abb:

    # mrmg "There's nothing quite like being in love with your best friend."
    mrmg "没有什么能比爱上自己的挚友更美好了。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:56
translate chinese mcgee18_f53975a4:

    # pc "It does seem nice."
    pc "听起来确实不错。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:59
translate chinese mcgee18_35c5f2a1:

    # "We get dressed and say our goodbyes."
    "我们穿好衣服，互相道别。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:60
translate chinese mcgee18_aea74b6e:

    # "Their relationship is a little strange, but damn they do love each other."
    "她们的关系有点奇怪，但天啊，她们确实深爱着对方。"

# game/Scenes/MrsMcGee/mrsmcgee18.rpy:61
translate chinese mcgee18_70b92f51:

    # "It must be nice to feel that close to another person. Maybe I will have something like that one day."
    "能和另一个人如此亲密，一定很美妙。也许有一天我也能拥有那样的感情。"

